<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Indeed no quotation marks, and that drives me crazy too. But I found little of that &quot;now wait who said what&quot; that I have found in other books that emp<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Indeed no quotation marks, and that drives me crazy too. But I found little of that "now wait who said what" that I have found in other books that employ this tactic. <br /><br />The quality of this book was of such that I could forgive the lack of quotation marks. I loved the book. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
